g.text: A positional rest variable used in <Atom>s, <Expr>s and <Plex>s. See
an extension point for specializations of the positional rest tag name. Stripe-skipping is not
<arg>: one argument of an atomic formula. See
an extension point for stripe skipping as well as specializations of the positional argument
Positional rest arguments follow the ordinary positional arguments in expressions in the normal-form serialization.
